Lost Dogs is a comedy drama about extortion, love, revenge, exile, destiny... and dogs. A couple of down and outs decide to make some easy cash by kidnapping a rich antique dealer's dogs and claiming the reward for finding them. This simple plan starts to go horribly wrong when they up the stakes and hold the dogs for ransom.

2005
Stars: Ron Moody, Lesley Joseph, Martin Trenaman, Tom Watt
